    <h1>Keyword Stuffing</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of unnaturally cramming a target keyword into content, meta tags, or alt text to manipulate search rankings. <strong>Google classifies it as spam</strong> and it consistently harms rather than helps rankings.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
